Package at.jku.swe.simcomp.commons.adaptor.endpoint

Class AdaptorEndpointController

java.lang.Object
at.jku.swe.simcomp.commons.adaptor.endpoint.AdaptorEndpointController
All Implemented Interfaces:
AdaptorEndpoint
@RestController public class AdaptorEndpointController extends Object implements AdaptorEndpoint
Class for endpoints acting as adaptors for simulations. Offers functionality for registration at the service-registry. And common endpoints. For registration, an environment variable SERVICE_REGISTRY_ENDPOINT has to point to the endpoint of the service-registry.
